{"id":"2225456e-6994-4e03-a96d-e0f898803dce","name":"Blade","description":"<p><strong><em>Puppet Master</em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\"> is an American </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Horror_film\" target=\"_blank\">horror film</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Film_series\" target=\"_blank\">series</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\"> which focuses on a group of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthropomorphic\" target=\"_blank\">anthropomorphic</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puppet\" target=\"_blank\">puppets</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\">animated by an </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egypt\" target=\"_blank\">Egyptian</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dark_Magic\" target=\"_blank\">spell</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\">, each equipped with its own unique and dangerous device and are represented as heroes, antiheroes and antagonists. The franchise was created by Charles Band and Kenneth J. Hall. The series consists of 15 films, 11 mainline, one </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crossover_(fiction)\" target=\"_blank\">crossover film</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34);\">, two spin-offs and a reboot.</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"UYo8iYMJdIoJ6JvsxHXEF.webp","creator":"Khaladar","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":23,"messages":529,"created_at":"2025-07-30T14:57:27.854181+00:00"}